name: kNight From Table
description: This Knight bust was hand carved by my Great Grandfather in the 1930's. The Knight has been standing guard atop one of the legs of a table that my GGF also carved. This piece will be the first NFT objkt in a series of 12 wooden busts digitized by 3D TrueDepth process. |  Twitter: @LowTechDigital | Audio by @Chad_XP
